						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab set up in the Śaṅkaraliṅga temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>Trailōkyamalla (Sōmēśvara I)—Date lost.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record belongs to the reign of <hi rend="bold">Trailōkyamalla</hi> and is assigned to <hi rend="bold">Sōmēśvara I</hi> on palaeographic grounds. It seems to register a gift of land. The date and other details are all lost.</p>						

